# Exome-Seq and Metabolomics Integration Analysis for Early-Onset Schizophrenia

[![License: MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT)

This repository contains code utilized in the integrative analysis of **exome sequencing (exome-seq)** and **metabolomics** data for **early-onset schizophrenia (EOS)**.

## Contents

1. [Variant & CNV Detection Pipeline](#1-variant--cnv-detection-pipeline)
2. [Differential Metabolite Analysis Pipeline](#2-differential-metabolite-analysis-pipeline)
3. [In-house R Scripts for Association Analyses](#3-in-house-r-scripts-for-association-analyses)

---

## 1. Variant & CNV Detection Pipeline

Pipeline to detect **single nucleotide variants (SNVs)** and **copy number variations (CNVs)** from exome-seq data.

## 2. Differential Metabolite Analysis Pipeline

Pipeline to detect **differentially expressed metabolites (DEMs)** from LC-MS/MS data.

## 3. In-house R Scripts for Association Analyses

| Analysis | Description | Script |
|----------|-------------|--------|
| (i) | Association between **gene variants** and **clinical symptom scores** | `R/variant_symptom_assoc.R` |
| (ii) | Correlation between **metabolite intensity** and **clinical symptom scores** | `R/metabolite_symptom_corr.R` |
| (iii) | Association between **gene variants** and **metabolite intensity** | `R/variant_metabolite_assoc.R` |
| (iv) | Construction of **protein-metabolite network** | `R/protein_metabolite_network.R` |

---

## Requirements

- **WGS/WES Pipeline**: [GATK](https://gatk.broadinstitute.org/), [CNVkit](https://cnvkit.readthedocs.io/), or similar
- **Metabolomics**: [XCMS](https://bioconductor.org/packages/release/bioc/html/xcms.html), [MetaboAnalystR](https://www.metaboanalyst.ca/)
- **R packages**: `tidyverse`, `limma`, `igraph`, `corrr`, `broom`

